name: Retroatalanta
description:
This free work is dedicated to the memory of the great Russian poet Boris Usov. He was the author of the lyrics for the Straw Raccoons group. Unfortunately, his texts have not yet been translated into any language other than Russian. If you have time, you can listen to the songs and read the lyrics here:

http://enoty.lenin.ru/

Boris also published fanzines. You can read them here:

https://vk.com/wall-30401645_96519
